{"tid":188531,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想撞鬼　嚴守日本旅行禁忌","createTime":"2017-04-05T17:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T12:03:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ed29541630dd81d8b037500c05e6d9022d98d4c","tid":188531,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170405/org/1491316746_3174.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170405%2Forg%2F1491316746_3174.jpg&h=7c3a6b78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/04/03/3314766/20170405_Vsub112new_clean_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F04%2F03%2F3314766%2F20170405_Vsub112new_clean_w.mp4&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5af256f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/04/03/3314766/20170405_Vsub112new_clean_w.mp4</a><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170405/large/05fa4044p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F05fa4044p.jpg&h=810a4bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Paul把多年對靈異和命案的研究，合成著作《日本靈探團》及《重大犯罪課》。 <br />\n <br />\n旅行的重點是遠離香港的都市壓力，人在異地可以鬆一鬆。外出玩到攰，回酒店當然要舒舒服服瞓番覺，但如果房間有些肉眼看不到的「污糟嘢」，那就出事了！日本罪案及靈異網台節目主持藍秀朗（Paul），坦言自小最愛研究神秘事，長大後貪刺激，喜歡到曾經鬧鬼的地點靈探，日本的自殺森林、赤軍基地、命案現場，他統統不放過，還出書大講靈異事件。 <br />\n <br />\n住盡各式酒店的Paul表示，有兩種房間「送都唔好住」，一是貼了神符的房，二是走廊尾房，因為很多時候靈體會積聚在尾房角落。房間望落乾淨，亦可能暗藏「污垢」。傳統說法是，靈體愛從後伏在人的肩膊上，所以進入房間後，身體感到異常疲倦，膊頭重重，就有可能是靈體在背後。不過Paul強調，舟車勞頓，又或者搭長途飛機，疲倦是在所難免，不要過度迷信。如果本身是吸煙者，在吸煙房內抽煙發現煙沒有向上飄，反而是向左右亂飄，又不是受冷氣風口影響，那麼房間也盡量避免居住了。<br />\n<br />\n入屋叫人，入廟拜神，不想撞鬼謹記要學懂禮貌。日本是禮儀之邦，在入酒店房前先敲敲門，接着說句打擾了，是對自己和「別人」的尊重。另外，日本人信奉神道教，深信帶備天然粗海鹽能潔淨負磁場，所以睡前可用小袋子把粗鹽綑好，再放枕頭底或床頭。寧可信其有，不可信其無，Paul再三強調，他不是怪力亂神，只是相信世上有鬼存在，自己不過是一個愛靈異故事的說書人，愛聽就聽，不愛也罷。「雖然我喜歡講靈異故事，但亦喜歡破除迷信。我認為人們常說的鬼古，有九成是創作或是誤會得來，所以凡事不要過度迷信，理性判斷就好了。」 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170405/large/05fa4055p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F05fa4055p.jpg&h=79b3348a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 有種說法指，入酒店房後膊頭重重，有可能是靈體伏在背後。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170405/large/05fa4022p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F05fa4022p.jpg&h=ff0e423a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Paul說住酒店時，宜先敲門，再講：「打擾了。」 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170405/large/05fa4033p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F05fa4033p.jpg&h=07b73d47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 日本人深信天然粗海鹽可潔淨負磁場，有助軀邪。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170405/large/05fa4011p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F05fa4011p.jpg&h=2db4c5fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Paul <br />\n <br />\n記者：劉芷晞<br />\n攝影：林栢鈞<br />\n編輯：蕭家慧<br />\n美術：黃創泰"},{"pid":"dc29aaf5f0d1d5a3ec1b4e64d14b838b52df07b0","tid":188531,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99075b47246e95aa025ef887c1edac2d777cc937","tid":188531,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:06:09.000Z","msg":"唔知睇邊套鬼片，有一幕係有隻鬼仔騎住個男人膊頭，跟住個男人話膊頭好酸<br />\n嗰幕個場景係熱鬧，唔陰森<br />\n驚咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482d40e208ab96cfdb656f6316122c8b31a87a73","tid":188531,"uid":53041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:13:41.000Z","msg":"打擾了 日文係咩?"},{"pid":"aee09ce33acf625e3d8aa3a072fef3c54c91baf5","tid":188531,"uid":71738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打擾了 日文係咩?</blockquote><br />\nsee me ma sei"},{"pid":"6ec8a44e6b0f67faf998e0897204c34641be28f4","tid":188531,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打擾了 日文係咩?</blockquote><br />\n其實要代多幾句打手擾了嘅其他語言，話哂住酒店喎，國際人士都會入去住，所以用日文講打打擾了係唔夠的"},{"pid":"49c8361c399320a4268e18b3a5b2124f45568bbb","tid":188531,"uid":12933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:31:53.000Z","msg":"海鹽定黃豆勁啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f1086b8a198ee8480c74306bdf2355f36dcdcf","tid":188531,"uid":10320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:36:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知睇邊套鬼片，有一幕係有隻鬼仔騎住個男人膊頭，跟住個男人話膊頭好酸<br />\n嗰幕個場景係熱鬧，唔陰森<br />\n驚咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依有d印像， 但又唔太記得"},{"pid":"1abec75422321d2708c12ba94c24347665a5eb42","tid":188531,"uid":6523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海鹽定黃豆勁啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黃豆係打日本傳統果隻鬼<br />\n唔係亡靈果隻鬼"},{"pid":"8bdc11d956cac36763b640b077af4c08d1ed8bdc","tid":188531,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打擾了 日文係咩?</blockquote><br />\nsee me ma sei</blockquote><br />\n餓渣媽屍媽s"},{"pid":"cccb0bd8e806316451911dd447fb5b2ff22c4edd","tid":188531,"uid":14899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score