31,"uid":53041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:44:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我之前住過京都町家都遇過怪事。</blockquote><br />\n可以講咩事嗎？</blockquote><br />\n町家部 cd player 個 volume 會自已去到最大，check in 冇幾耐已經試過一次，第二日我地出左門口到返黎入屋廳個枱面就有張咁既留言。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i238.photobucket.com/albums/ff47/ashleyroad/KYOTO%202015/9496C266-A366-4321-BCE0-C8ED0A131E90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi238.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fff47%2Fashleyroad%2FKYOTO%25202015%2F9496C266-A366-4321-BCE0-C8ED0A131E90.jpg&h=706457ff&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n部機自己開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21eb8c5518a33e99b9f5cf59ac8d43a03b20c9d0","tid":188531,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:49:33.000Z","msg":"諗起之前自己一個去東京<br />\n分咗去尾房 一入去就好唔舒服<br />\n跟住又突然之間有種好想喊嘅感覺<br />\n床前面有塊大鏡 覺得塊鏡有啲嘢咁<br />\n就搵塊浴巾遮住佢 跟住明顯感覺好好多"},{"pid":"cec6c7d5cc30625f50e22350ac6734cecf7a9b14","tid":188531,"uid":8986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:50:56.000Z","msg":"黎緊諗住一個人去旅行 <br />\n但係好驚一個人住酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200c46b94b3ef02ec03bc6608939563fc31f2006","tid":188531,"uid":39431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:55:45.000Z","msg":"我差唔多每一次次旅行 總會有一晚撞正住尾房<br />\n年頭係福岡一個人訓尾房都冇事 , 好正常<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係屋企仲大獲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a2b921a1a6386a8b9b44a9c5cd4283511fcd2f","tid":188531,"uid":79485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打擾了 日文係咩?</blockquote><br />\n其實要代多幾句打手擾了嘅其他語言，話哂住酒店喎，國際人士都會入去住，所以用日文講打打擾了係唔夠的</blockquote><br />\n打擾了 的日文係輸你媽借"},{"pid":"1cff750c386f7840e952db968502d8884ff0bc92","tid":188531,"uid":5786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:02:28.00