r />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/04/03/3314766/20170405_Vsub112new_clean_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F04%2F03%2F3314766%2F20170405_Vsub112new_clean_w.mp4&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5af256f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/04/03/3314766/20170405_Vsub112new_clean_w.mp4</a><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170405/large/05fa4044p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F05fa4044p.jpg&h=810a4bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Paul把多年對靈異和命案的研究，合成著作《日本靈探團》及《重大犯罪課》。 <br />\n <br />\n旅行的重點是遠離香港的都市壓力，人在異地可以鬆一鬆。外出玩到攰，回酒店當然要舒舒服服瞓番覺，但如果房間有些肉眼看不到的「污糟嘢」，那就出事了！日本罪案及靈異網台節目主持藍秀朗（Paul），坦言自小最愛研究神秘事，長大後貪刺激，喜歡到曾經鬧鬼的地點靈探，日本的自殺森林、赤軍基地、命案現場，他統統不放過，還出書大講靈異事件。 <br />\n <br />\n住盡各式酒店的Paul表示，有兩種房間「送都唔好住」，一是貼了神符的房，二是走廊尾房，因為很多時候靈體會積聚在尾房角落。房間望落乾淨，亦可能暗藏「污垢」。傳統說法是，靈體愛從後伏在人的肩膊上，所以進入房間後，身體感到異常疲倦，膊頭重重，就有可能是靈體在背後。不過Paul強調，舟車勞頓，又或者搭長途飛機，疲倦是在所難免，不要過度迷信。如果本身是吸煙者，在吸煙房內<span style=\"color: red;\">抽煙發現煙沒有向上飄，反而是向左右亂飄，又不是受冷氣風口影響，那</span>麼房間也盡量避免居住了。<br />\n<br />\n入屋叫人，入廟拜神，不想撞鬼謹記要學懂禮貌。日本是禮儀之邦，在入酒店房前先敲敲門，接着說句打擾了，是對自己和「別人」的尊重。另外，日本人信奉神道教，深信帶備天然粗海鹽能潔淨負磁場，所以睡前可用小袋子把粗鹽綑好，再放枕頭底或床頭。寧可信其有，不可信其無，Paul再三強調，他不是怪力亂神，只是相信世上有鬼存在，自己不過是一個愛靈異故事的說書人，愛聽就聽，不愛也罷。「雖然我喜歡講靈異故事，但亦喜歡破除迷信。我認為人們常說的鬼古，有九成是創作或是誤會得來，所以凡事不要過度迷信，理性判斷就好了。」 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170405/large/05fa4055p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F05fa4055p.jpg&h=79b3348a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 有種說法指，入酒店房後膊頭重重，有可能是靈體伏在背後。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170405/large/05fa4022p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F05fa4022p.jpg&h=ff0e423a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Paul說住酒店時，宜先敲門，再講：「打擾了。」 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170405/large/05fa4033p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F05fa4033p.jpg&h=07b73d47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 日本人深信天然粗海鹽可潔淨負磁場，有助軀邪。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170405/large/05fa4011p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F05fa4011p.jpg&h=2db4c5fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Paul <br />\n <br />\n記者：劉芷晞<br />\n攝影：林栢鈞<br />\n編輯：蕭家慧<br />\n美術：黃創泰</blockquote><br />\n可否解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63eed0cf1e5ba32ba1a8799c03dc21c8d6c61d2","tid":188531,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[quote]唔知睇邊套鬼片，有一幕係有隻鬼仔騎住個男人膊頭，跟住個男人話膊頭好酸<br />\n嗰幕個場景係熱鬧，唔陰森<br />\n驚咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依有d印像， 但又唔太記得</blockquote><br />\n泰國片，鬼影，呢套好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote<br />\n隻女鬼一直騎住係男主膊頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講緊鬼仔同熱鬧<br />\n點會係鬼影阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鬼影一 d 都唔熱鬧，莫非&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n係咪搞乜鬼奪命雜作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有d印象，都係泰國片黎，不過隻鬼個口係爆開左，個男仔本身同班fd一齊係間房玩緊<br />\n人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都記得係泰國片 個仔去磅重 重左好多<br />\n睇醫生搵唔到原因 因為個女騎住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6e126a6c81e76894ce48cefc950902e520e5fd","tid":188531,"uid":34654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:14:14.000Z","msg":"我媽咪之前去大阪住民宿<br />\n訓訓下痛醒左 話有人cool住佢條頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b99d9e5335636f49cc1d22c0f5bd21ed14793b0","tid":188531,"uid":16096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:18:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔知睇邊套鬼片，有一幕係有隻鬼仔騎住個男人膊頭，跟住個男人話膊頭好酸<br />\n嗰幕個場景係熱鬧，唔陰森<br />\n驚咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依有d印像， 但又唔太記得</blockquote><br />\n泰國片，鬼影，呢套好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係泰國片，印象中記得個男主角係做攝影師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鬼影男主角唔係攝影師咩<br />\n成日曬相 有一攤光左"},{"pid":"ffc15f59e804627cd44577497a8f50e4d1578cd8","tid":188531,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我之前住過京都町家都遇過怪事。</blockquote><br />\n可以講咩事嗎？</blockquote><br />\n町家部 cd player 個 volume 會自已去到最大，check in 冇幾耐已經試過一次，第二日我地出左門口到返黎入屋廳個枱面就有張咁既留言。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i238.photobucket.com/albums/ff47/ashleyroad/KYOTO%202015/9496C266-A366-4321-BCE0-C8ED0A131E90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi238.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fff47%2Fashleyroad%2FKYOTO%25202015%2F9496C266-A366-4321-BCE0-C8ED0A131E90.jpg&h=706457ff&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n部機自己開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n check in 時部機本身開住播住 d jazz music，但冇幾耐部機個 volume 忽然校到最大，嚇到我即刻熄左機。到第二日出門，行完返到黎入屋廳張枱就有段咁既留言，我估部機係清潔執房後開返，跟著又自動校大個 volume。到而家我唯有安慰自已係部 bose 壞左，而呢間町家 check in 時個 staff 介紹返間屋同擺設有過百年歷史，心諗會唔會有好多 friend 陪我一齊住。"},{"pid":"840a23f714a88260c944d8e0285ffe7f6fa32c45","tid":188531,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我之前住過京都町家都遇過怪事。</blockquote><br />\n可以講咩事嗎？</blockquote><br />\n町家部 cd player 個 volume 會自已去到最大，check in 冇幾耐已經試過一次，第二日我地出左門口到返黎入屋廳個枱面就有張咁既留言。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i238.photobucket.com/albums/ff47/ashleyroad/KYOTO%202015/9496C266-A366-4321-BCE0-C8ED0A131E90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi238.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fff47%2Fashleyroad%2FKYOTO%25202015%2F9496C266-A366-4321-BCE0-C8ED0A131E90.jpg&h=706457ff&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你地根本不在屋內，佢報驚都冇意思喎。<br />\n而且咁寫俾你，荒死你唔知道咁好似。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616f0a9d1213cb85f6ec6264b698ca1ce45571a4","tid":188531,"uid":97277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:25:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打擾了 日文係咩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSu mi ma sen, o jia ma si ma su<br />\n<br />\n咁樣讀<br />\n意思：不好意思，打擾了"}]}